'''中華菊头蝠'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Rhinolophus sinicus''}}）是[[翼手目|翼手目]][[菊頭蝠科|菊頭蝠科]]的一種蝙蝠，分布于[[中国南方|中国南方]]、[[印度|印度]]、[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]、[[越南|越南]]等地<ref name = "Filatov2013">{{cite journal | last1 = Filatov | first1 = Dmitry A. | last2 = Mao | first2 = Xiuguang | last3 = He | first3 = Guimei | last4 = Zhang | first4 = Junpeng | last5 = Rossiter | first5 = Stephen J. | last6 = Zhang | first6 = Shuyi | title = Lineage Divergence and Historical Gene Flow in the Chinese Horseshoe Bat (''Rhinolophus sinicus'') | journal = PLOS ONE | volume = 8 | issue = 2 | year = 2013 | pages = e56786 | issn = 1932-6203 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0056786| pmid = 23451086 | pmc = 3581519 | bibcode = 2013PLoSO...856786M }}{{Open access}}</ref>，过去一度被視为[[鲁氏菊头蝠|鲁氏菊头蝠]]的华东亚种（Rhinolophus rouxii sinicus）。近年来在染色体、形态方面研究，表明其与鲁氏菊头蝠有很大的差异，因而被提升为一独立种<ref>{{cite journal|author=徐伟霞、周昭敏、章敬旗、吴毅、李玉春、胡锦矗|title=中华菊头蝠头骨形态特征地理差异的研究|journal=四川动物|year=2005|volume=4}}</ref><ref>Chiroptera Specialist Group 2000.  [http://www.iucnredlist.org/search/details.php/41529/all Rhinolophus sinicus].   [http://www.iucnredlist.org 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/ |date=20180508171911 |dateformat=iso }}  Downloaded on 30 July 2007.</ref>。

其[[种加词|种加词]]“''Sinicus''”意为“中华的”。

==外型==
中華菊头蝠的前肢長4.3至5.6公分，耳長1.5至2公分，尾長2.1至3公分，為體型中等的菊頭蝠，背側的毛有兩色，基部為棕色至白色，頂端1/3則為紅棕色；腹側的毛色較背側淡。本種與鲁氏菊头蝠外型相似但翅膀較其稍長，與[[托氏菊頭蝠|托氏菊頭蝠]]形似但體型稍大<ref name="Smith"/>。

==生態==
中華菊头蝠為[[社會性動物|社會性動物]]，一般棲息於洞窟中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bio.bris.ac.uk/research/bats/China%20bats/rhinolophussinicus.htm|title=Rhinolophus sinicus|website=University of Bristol - School of Biological Sciences|accessdate=2021-05-20|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224165053/http://www.bio.bris.ac.uk/research/bats/China%20bats/rhinolophussinicus.htm}}</ref>，其群體可能由數隻至數百隻蝙蝠組成，繁殖季時懷孕、哺乳中的雌蝠會組成{{le|生殖群集|Maternity colony}}<ref name="Smith">{{cite book| url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sgQsHR-WnTUC| title=Mammals of China| editor1-first=Andrew T.| editor1-last=Smith| editor2-first=Yan| editor2-last=Xie| year=2013| publisher=Princeton University Press| isbn=9781400846887| pages=231–232| access-date=2021-06-12| archive-date=2020-06-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621044544/https://books.google.com/books?id=sgQsHR-WnTUC}}</ref>。{{le|中国洞蛭属|Sinospelaeobdella}}的山蛭在洞窟中吸取中華菊头蝠等數種蝙蝠的血為食<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Huang|first=Taifu|last2=Liu|first2=Zhiwei|last3=Gong|first3=Xiaoyan|last4=Wu|first4=Tao|last5=Liu|first5=Hui|last6=Deng|first6=Jiaxin|last7=Zhang|first7=Youxiang|last8=Peng|first8=Qingzhong|last9=Zhang|first9=Libiao|last10=Liu|first10=Zhixiao|date=2019-02-25|title=Vampire in the darkness: a new genus and species of land leech exclusively bloodsucking cave-dwelling bats from China (Hirudinda: Arhynchobdellida: Haemadipsidae)|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31716579/|journal=Zootaxa|volume=4560|issue=2|pages=zootaxa.4560.2.2|doi=10.11646/zootaxa.4560.2.2|issn=1175-5334|pmid=31716579|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-date=2021-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210612022956/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31716579/}}</ref>。

==冠状病毒宿主==
2005年[[香港大学|香港大学]]的研究人员就在中华菊头蝠身上发现與[[SARS-CoV|SARS-CoV]]相似的病毒株（[[SARSr-CoV|SARSr-CoV]]）[[蝙蝠冠狀病毒HKU3|HKU3]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/Taxonomy/Browser/wwwtax.cgi?mode=Undef&id=442736&lvl=3&keep=1&srchmode=1&unlock|title=Bat SARS coronavirus HKU3|publisher=[[NCBI|NCBI]] Taxonomy  Browser}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uniprot.org/proteomes/UP000007450|title=Bat coronavirus HKU3 (BtCoV) (SARS-like coronavirus HKU3)|publisher=[[Uniprot|Uniprot]]|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413064702/https://www.uniprot.org/proteomes/UP000007450|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2013年又有[[WIV1病毒|WIV1]]和[[SHC014病毒|SHC014]]兩個SARSr-CoV病毒株在中華菊頭蝠樣本中發現<ref name="GeLi2013">{{cite journal|last1=Ge|first1=Xing-Yi|last2=Li|first2=Jia-Lu|last3=Yang|first3=Xing-Lou|last4=Chmura|first4=Aleksei A.|last5=Zhu|first5=Guangjian|last6=Epstein|first6=Jonathan H.|last7=Mazet|first7=Jonna K.|last8=Hu|first8=Ben|last9=Zhang|first9=Wei|last10=Peng|first10=Cheng|last11=Zhang|first11=Yu-Ji|last12=Luo|first12=Chu-Ming|last13=Tan|first13=Bing|last14=Wang|first14=Ning|last15=Zhu|first15=Yan|last16=Crameri|first16=Gary|last17=Zhang|first17=Shu-Yi|last18=Wang|first18=Lin-Fa|last19=Daszak|first19=Peter|last20=Shi|first20=Zheng-Li|display-authors=8|title=Isolation and characterization of a bat SARS-like coronavirus that uses the ACE2 receptor|journal=Nature|volume=503|issue=7477|year=2013|pages=535–538|issn=0028-0836|doi=10.1038/nature12711}}</ref>，[[香港大学医学院|香港大学医学院]]传染病学教授[[袁国勇|袁国勇]]称，SARS病毒的天然宿主为中华菊头蝠，而[[果子狸|果子狸]]只是SARS病毒（[[果子狸SARS冠狀病毒|果子狸SARS冠狀病毒]]）的[[中間宿主|中間宿主]]<ref>{{cite news|title=科学家进一步证实SARS病毒来源于中华菊头蝠|url=http://news.sciencenet.cn//htmlpaper/2013103111232312930888.shtm|accessdate=2013-11-16|newspaper=中国科学网|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924215900/http://news.sciencenet.cn//htmlpaper/2013103111232312930888.shtm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年美國[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]大學的[[拉爾夫·S·巴里克|拉爾夫·S·巴里克]]與[[武漢病毒研究所|武漢病毒研究所]]的[[石正麗|石正麗]]實驗室合作，以重組病毒實驗發現SHC014病毒有感染人類的潛力，研究人員指新病毒致病性高，不過是否會像SARS般人傳人仍需更多研究闡明<ref name="pmid26552008">{{cite journal| author=Menachery VD, Yount BL, Debbink K, Agnihothram S, Gralinski LE, Plante JA | display-authors=etal| title=A SARS-like cluster of circulating bat coronaviruses shows potential for human emergence. | journal=Nat Med | year= 2015 | volume= 21 | issue= 12 | pages= 1508-13 | pmid=26552008 | doi=10.1038/nm.3985 | pmc=4797993 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=26552008  }} </ref>。2016年，石正麗實驗室在雲南的中華菊頭蝠中發現另一SARSr-CoV病毒株[[WIV16病毒|WIV16]]，全基因組序列與SARS-CoV的相似度為96%<ref name="pmid26719272">{{cite journal | author=Yang XL, Hu B, Wang B, Wang MN, Zhang Q, Zhang W | display-authors=etal | title=Isolation and Characterization of a Novel Bat Coronavirus Closely Related to the Direct Progenitor of Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus. | journal=J Virol | year=2016 | volume=90 | issue=6 | pages=3253-6 | pmid=26719272 | doi=10.1128/JVI.02582-15 | pmc=4810638 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=26719272 | access-date=2022-05-24 | archive-date=2021-07-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709094528/https://misuse.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/error/abuse.shtml?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org%2Fcite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=26719272 }}</ref>。

2018年4月，石正麗實驗室發表了提出感染豬隻的新型冠狀病毒[[猪急性腹泻综合征冠状病毒|猪急性腹泻综合征冠状病毒]]（SADS-CoV），可能源自感染中華菊頭蝠的[[菊頭蝠冠狀病毒HKU2|菊頭蝠冠狀病毒HKU2]]<ref name="pmid29618817">{{cite journal| author=Zhou P, Fan H, Lan T, Yang XL, Shi WF, Zhang W | display-authors=etal| title=Fatal swine acute diarrhoea syndrome caused by an HKU2-related coronavirus of bat origin. | journal=Nature | year= 2018 | volume= 556 | issue= 7700 | pages= 255-258 | pmid=29618817 | doi=10.1038/s41586-018-0010-9 | pmc=7094983 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=29618817  }} </ref>。

